{"tid":2140912,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"由今日起我盡量幫襯多啲龍門，並拒絕幫襯人渣哥為首既分化狗","createTime":"2020-08-05T10:07:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T09:16:59.000Z","uid":58335,"like":355,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"f201e88fabd23daa7a9dddc3dbcb769a69b046f1","tid":2140912,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:07:44.000Z","msg":"龍門：人渣哥捐十萬？我跟，再大返你四十萬！Total 五十萬！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2140809\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2140809</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇左個po<br />\n見到老世喊<br />\n都覺得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人渣哥、水門閪係咪要迫死佢你哋先開心？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n論食物<br />\nD人成日話龍門難食<br />\n初期可能唔係幾好食<br />\n但而家已經同茶記冇分別<br />\n又大份又抵食<br />\n人渣哥d野你估好好食咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n論人品<br />\n我覺得張老闆人品點都好過個班撚樣<br />\n比人屈咁耐人格謀殺都冇出聲<br />\n係到今日終於頂唔順<br />\n張生有冇屈你人渣哥同振美有關係呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n從今以後<br />\n唔會幫襯所有人渣哥為首既分化狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你哋慢慢做清算師啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果佢哋真係有做過用錢引龍門員工抹黑既話<br />\n佢哋仲衰過啲藍店<br />\n咁撚賤嘅嘢都做得出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n等睇話我龍門pr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d76b0d03dbc07db08ddc3dd841ae0f6e1054c8fa","tid":2140912,"uid":301989,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得龍門好慘 日日俾人屈 又話偽黃又話黑社會 依家仲要屈埋強姦 cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f4d980d8ffda2cbfb1516434d04e9e782448b3","tid":2140912,"uid":58335,"like":59,"dislike":4,"score":55,"quote":{"pid":"d76b0d03dbc07db08ddc3dd841ae0f6e1054c8fa","tid":2140912,"uid":301989,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T10:13:53.000Z","msg":"不嬲都覺得龍門好慘 日日俾人屈 又話偽黃又話黑社會 依家仲要屈埋強姦 cls<img src=\"/asset